Contains tools useful for data screening, testing moderation (Cohen et. al. 2003)<doi:10.4324/9780203774441>, mediation (MacKinnon et. al. 2002)<doi:10.1037/1082-989x.7.1.83> and estimating power (Murphy & Myors 2014)<ISBN:9781315773155>.

name: r-quantpsyc
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.6' %}

{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-quantpsyc
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/QuantPsyc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/QuantPsyc/QuantPsyc_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d86bf3733560272c74abf2d8c176498ea6e094fe1600a4787467a072c14072b5

build:
  number: 4
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip  # [win]

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-boot
    - r-dplyr
    - r-purrr

  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-boot
    - r-dplyr
    - r-purrr

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('QuantPsyc')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('QuantPsyc')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=QuantPsyc
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Contains tools useful for data screening, testing moderation (Cohen et. al. 2003)<doi:10.4324/9780203774441>,
    mediation (MacKinnon et. al. 2002)<doi:10.1037/1082-989x.7.1.83> and estimating
    power (Murphy & Myors 2014)<ISBN:9781315773155>.
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - thewchan
